"1 tablespoon olive oil","4  (6-ounce) bone-in short ribs, trimmed","3/4 teaspoon kosher salt, divided","1/2 teaspoon freshly ground black pepper, divided","2 cups finely chopped onion","3/4 cup finely chopped carrot","1/2 cup finely chopped celery","8  garlic cloves, minced","2 cups water","2 tablespoons tomato paste","1/2 teaspoon dried basil","1/2 teaspoon dried oregano","1  (28-ounce) can unsalted whole tomatoes","12 ounces uncooked pappardelle or whole-wheat fettuccine"